@startuml
!include ../plantuml-theme.iuml
left to right direction

title 图 3.3 权限映射关系图

rectangle "用户属性\nrole\nuserId\nprimaryOrg\ndirectTags" as UserAttr
rectangle "有效标签展开\nEffectiveTags(u)" as Effective
rectangle "文档元数据\nowner\norgTag\nisPublic" as DocMeta
rectangle "可见性规则\nADMIN -> all\nUSER -> owner OR isPublic OR orgTag in EffectiveTags(u)" as Rule
rectangle "可见范围\nVisible Scope V(u)" as Visible

UserAttr --> Effective
UserAttr --> Rule
Effective --> Rule
DocMeta --> Rule
Rule --> Visible

legend bottom
“公开访问”应由文档属性 isPublic 表达，
不要再用 Primary: PUBLIC 代替公开语义。
endlegend
@enduml
